# Review: APPROVED ✅
**Files:** `src/ui/issues.rs`, `src/app.rs` | **Date:** 2026-05-27 | **VAULT ref:** 2026-05-27-005-review-multi-select-issues.md

## TL;DR
**Status:** APPROVED
